data.name: richTextBoxManipulationSample.Text
data.value:
This is the PenumbraPhysics.Manipulation sample!
Use the [Scroll Wheel] of your mouse to scroll this text. Use your [Left Mouse Button] to drag / manipulate the physics object. -> If you want to see the physics, then enable that option in the "Settings" drop down. Use your [Right Mouse Button] to open the context menu of the editor. Click on the "Close" button to close this message.
